title: Pure Heart by Lenny LeBlanc
description:
Beautiful Praise and Worship Music by Lenny Leblanc

The album is a wonderful worship time -- a calm, peaceful, and intimate worship experience in more of a 60&#039;s-70&#039;s folk music style. It is very focused on Jesus, and a deeper relationship with Him. Listening to it has been a great comfort and strength to me, especially at difficult times in my life.
